See what others have to say about
Devaney’s
Friendliest staff anywhere. Great entertainment almost any night of the week. Food is quick and delicious, plus drink specials galore. You can’t go wrong with Devaney’s.
Jorge O
A great place to go relax, catch a game, grab some grub, and mingle with friendly locals. Fun night time atmosphere varies between Dirty bingo, trivia, kareoke and the big game is always on one of its many flat screens. Worth your time to visit.
Travis S
Great beer selection! That’s the best part of experience!
